---
import "@/styles/global.css";
import BaseLayout from "@/components/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  SEOTitle="Audit Trails | PrincipalAI"
  SEODescription="Traceable AI workflows that improve transparency, accountability, governance, and decision assurance."
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#071f3f] via-[#123f86] to-[#e8f4ff] px-8 py-24 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-blue-100">
        Audit Trails
      </p>

      <h1 class="max-w-5xl font-serif text-5xl font-bold leading-tight sm:text-6xl">
        Understand how decisions were reached.
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
        PrincipalAI helps organisations maintain visibility over AI-assisted workflows through traceability, evidence tracking, review records, and structured decision histories.
      </p>

      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700"
      >
        Request a demonstration
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main>
    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            The challenge
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Trust depends on understanding what happened.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            As AI becomes part of organisational workflows, decision-makers need visibility into how information was used, what evidence supported conclusions, and what reviews occurred before outputs were accepted.
          </p>

          <p>
            Without traceability, it becomes difficult to explain decisions, demonstrate governance, or learn from previous work.
          </p>

          <p>
            Audit trails provide a structured record of how AI-assisted outputs were generated, reviewed, and approved.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
          What audit trails provide
        </p>

        <h2 class="max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
          Greater transparency across AI-enabled workflows.
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Evidence tracking
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Record which documents, datasets, models, and knowledge sources informed outputs and recommendations.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Workflow history
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Maintain visibility over key stages of analysis, review, approval, and decision-making.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Review records
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Document who reviewed outputs, what feedback was provided, and how recommendations evolved.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Governance support
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Strengthen accountability and support organisational governance requirements.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            Example applications
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Designed for environments where decisions must be defensible.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Policy advice and regulatory submissions requiring evidence transparency.
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Infrastructure and investment decisions involving multiple reviews and stakeholders.
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Technical reports and analytical outputs where assumptions and sources must be documented.
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            AI-assisted organisational workflows requiring accountability and governance oversight.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            Why PrincipalAI
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Transparency designed into the system.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            PrincipalAI treats auditability as part of responsible AI design, not as an afterthought.
          </p>

          <p>
            Our systems are designed to connect evidence, workflows, review processes, and organisational governance into a coherent decision-support environment.
          </p>

          <p>
            This helps organisations strengthen confidence in AI-assisted work while maintaining accountability and professional standards.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-[#071f3f] px-8 py-20 text-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl text-center">
        <h2 class="mx-auto max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight">
          Build AI workflows that can be explained, reviewed, and trusted.
        </h2>

        <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
          Talk to PrincipalAI about audit trails, governance, traceability, and decision assurance for AI-enabled operations.
        </p>

        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700"
        >
          Request a demonstration
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
